- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the satisfiability and model-checking problems for a temporal logic extension. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the verification of properties in a programming context. 
- cs.LT (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with the specification and verification of temporal properties. 
- cs.FL (Formal Methods) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of formal methods for verification. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the verification of software properties.
